workflow.name: Create complete 20-song YouTube playlists with Suno API, Claude & Telegram bot
workflow.description:
![AUTOMATE 2.png](fileId:1750)
**Transform your music creation process with this comprehensive automated system that generates complete playlists from simple text descriptions!**

## üöÄ What You Get

This professional-grade N8N workflow system automatically creates **20 unique songs per playlist** (40 total tracks with 2 versions each) using cutting-edge AI technology. Simply describe your desired playlist through Telegram, and watch as the system generates song ideas, writes lyrics, produces audio, and organizes everything in Google Drive.

## ‚ö° Key Features

- **ü§ñ Telegram Bot Interface** - User-friendly chat interface for playlist creation
- **üéº AI Song Generation** - 20 unique song titles and descriptions per playlist
- **üìù Automated Lyrics Writing** - Professional-quality lyrics for each song
- **üéµ Audio Production** - High-quality music tracks via Suno AI
- **üìÅ Organized Storage** - Automatic Google Drive folder management
- **üîÑ Complete Automation** - End-to-end workflow with minimal manual intervention

## üõ†Ô∏è APIs & Services Used

- **Telegram Bot API** - User interaction interface
- **Claude AI (Anthropic)** - Song ideation and lyrics generation
- **Suno AI** - Professional music track generation
- **Google Sheets** - Database management
- **Google Drive** - Automated file storage and organization
- **Google Apps Script** - Seamless file upload integration

## üì¶ What's Included

‚úÖ **7 Complete N8N Workflows** - Ready-to-import automation system
‚úÖ **Comprehensive Setup Guide** - Step-by-step installation instructions
‚úÖ **Google Sheets Database Template** - Pre-configured data structure
‚úÖ **Google Apps Script Code** - Custom Drive upload functionality
‚úÖ **AI Prompt Templates** - Optimized system messages for all agents
‚úÖ **Troubleshooting Guide** - Solutions for common issues
‚úÖ **Customization Instructions** - Modify outputs to match your style

## üí° Perfect For

- Music producers and content creators
- Playlist curators and music enthusiasts
- Digital agencies offering music services
- Developers interested in AI automation
- Anyone looking to streamline music creation workflows

## üéØ System Requirements

- Active N8N instance (cloud or self-hosted)
- API access to: Telegram, Claude AI, Suno AI, Google Services
- Basic understanding of N8N workflows (setup guide included)

## üí∞ Cost Considerations

- **Suno AI**: ~240 credits per playlist (20 songs √ó 2 versions)
- **Claude AI**: Variable based on usage
- **Other APIs**: Minimal costs for most use cases

## ‚è±Ô∏è Expected Processing Time

Complete playlist generation: **30-45 minutes** per playlist (fully automated)

---

**üéÅ Bonus: Complete documentation includes AI agent customization guide, allowing you to fine-tune song styles, lyrics generation, and bot behavior to match your specific needs.**

*Get instant access to this powerful automation system and start generating professional playlists today!*

---

If you need a csutom workflow please reach out via email joseph@uppfy.com

data.details:
The IF node can be used to implement binary conditional logic in your workflow. You can set up one-to-many conditions to evaluate each item of data being inputted into the node. That data will either evaluate to TRUE or FALSE and route out of the node accordingly.

This node has multiple types of conditions: Bool, String, Number, and Date & Time.
